{"tid":1798193,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"韓國瑜稱若當選 年青人出國讀書 一年資助100萬","createTime":"2019-12-26T04:56:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T07:45:06.000Z","uid":144372,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"76db5fbe09b0f7a171f02ecdde356e817e546a4c","tid":1798193,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T04:56:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20191225/1610411.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20191225%2F1610411.htm&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=9a6c5770\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20191225/1610411.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜強調，「為何年輕人不喜歡韓國瑜？而老年人不喜歡蔡英文？」盼外界思考，他認為，民進黨要好好檢討中老年人為什麼不支持蔡英文，而年輕人如果越瞭解候選人，就越會投韓國瑜，因為最關心年輕人就是韓國瑜。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜也指出，接下來會大力投資年輕人，啟動國家人才培養的建設，送大學生出國交換一年，一個學生補助100萬，這個計畫叫做「人才大培育計畫」、「滿天星計畫」，每個年輕人像星星 ，政府在你年輕推你一把，一年後接受這個計畫的朋友，第一語言進步，二解決困難問題的程度增加，三交朋友的能力增加，四年輕人變勇敢。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜說，對年輕人來說，沒有勇敢就會往後退，所以特別重視年輕人勇敢，估計一年政府要花400億，政策公開後吸引許多企業捐款，很多華僑聽到這個計畫，更主動說可以讓出國的學生住我的房子，他強調，「年輕朋友越瞭解政見，一定會投韓國瑜。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 年輕支持者少&hellip;韓國瑜反問蔡英文 「為何中老年人支持者少？」 | ETtoday政治 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20191225/1610411.htm#ixzz69Ba97N2O\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20191225%2F1610411.htm%23ixzz69Ba97N2O&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=e2d48501\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20191225/1610411.htm#ixzz69Ba97N2O</a><br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"f21d9029b8d8db16f91aa3e6cf6dbb1f05fc4ea4","tid":1798193,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T04:58:00.000Z","msg":"信口開河"},{"pid":"44e64d89da5f15fca4e7e7b51bea8ba5b69665b7","tid":1798193,"uid":49336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f21d9029b8d8db16f91aa3e6cf6dbb1f05fc4ea4","tid":1798193,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T04:58:00.000Z","msg":"信口開河"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67rjKPT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67rjKPT.jpg&h=c3cec167&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a97e5825df6bdf591d553e6598f11bb9ba1e440e","tid":1798193,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:02:30.000Z","msg":"講咗 當做咗"},{"pid":"c03b76809082f37f7d94f014573d884522b2a48d","tid":1798193,"uid":277743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:03:56.000Z","msg":"高雄又話搞經濟 成果呢?"},{"pid":"7fe392bb17a743b2edd85ea8d1c480b8a3f91f94","tid":1798193,"uid":267178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:19:43.000Z","msg":"台灣本地讀書都未免費，點解要補助出國讀書？出國讀書唔係應該俾有錢人或者有獎學金嘅人讀？"},{"pid":"c50403a80796e41d1a80224060cd4a54d8f3de9e","tid":1798193,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fe392bb17a743b2edd85ea8d1c480b8a3f91f94","tid":1798193,"uid":267178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:19:43.000Z","msg":"台灣本地讀書都未免費，點解要補助出國讀書？出國讀書唔係應該俾有錢人或者有獎學金嘅人讀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T07:20:44.000Z","msg":"補助你去支那 咁都唔明呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f634e688c7e1117d5fec598d66f14d21c018b303","tid":1798193,"uid":267178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c50403a80796e41d1a80224060cd4a54d8f3de9e","tid":1798193,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fe392bb17a743b2edd85ea8d1c480b8a3f91f94","tid":1798193,"uid":267178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:19:43.000Z","msg":"台灣本地讀書都未免費，點解要補助出國讀書？出國讀書唔係應該俾有錢人或者有獎學金嘅人讀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T07:20:44.000Z","msg":"補助你去支那 咁都唔明呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T07:45:06.000Z","msg":"我嘅意思係都要對外俾個合理理由㗎。例如批多啲獎學金俾成績好嘅